  "content": "<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Lazy-load mediabunny on web by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11094\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11094</a></li>\n<li>Fix Android crash in chat keyboard scroll (part 2) by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11096\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11096</a></li>\n<li>Bump golang.org/x/crypto from 0.51.0 to 0.52.0 in /bskyweb by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11100\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11100</a></li>\n<li>Add more search placeholders by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11089\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11089</a></li>\n<li>Revert &quot;Add more search placeholders (<a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11089\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11089</a>)&quot; by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11101\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11101</a></li>\n<li>Bump version to v1.128.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11105\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11105</a></li>\n<li>Adjust AA device signals copy by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11106\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11106</a></li>\n<li>Update advanced search UI by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11088\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11088</a></li>\n<li>use source file for web video compression by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11090\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11090</a></li>\n<li>Update mergeRefs util for React 19 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11108\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11108</a></li>\n<li>Revert &quot;Remove <code>react-native-dotenv</code> (<a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10706</a>)&quot; by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11110\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11110</a></li>\n<li>Fix search typeahead performance with absolute overlay by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11103\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11103</a></li>\n<li>v1.127.1 Release prep by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11116\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11116</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/compare/1.127.0...1.127.1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.127.0...1.127.1</a></p>",
